{"tid":2357384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉違國安法50多人陸續准保釋","createTime":"2021-01-07T11:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T12:57:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0acbb717b2a6d5d1879dfc4548a396a0554aca15","tid":2357384,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569198-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569198-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z5ktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=3e018905\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569198-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=35b28ce3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569198-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕50多名發起或參與去年民主派初選人士，指他們涉嫌違反《香港國安法》。消息指，區諾軒和關尚義已先後保釋，其餘大部分被捕人士，將陸續獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n正在服刑的前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒亦涉嫌違反《香港國安法》被捕，被安排到荔枝角懲教所錄口供。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨前主席胡志偉，因涉及違反另一宗案的保釋條件，案件明天審理，需要還押。"},{"pid":"5fd8ce3611a54694c667dc98d857edb5a95f8299","tid":2357384,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:42:40.000Z","msg":"又話好歹毒計劃？<br />\n<br />\n咁歹毒又可以保釋？"},{"pid":"4973ad07f5b1f6976e15fbe5992e700f52f7b4a6","tid":2357384,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />技安法"},{"pid":"1f25686f128b50efc95850a7b38a7aaf05591e0a","tid":2357384,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/07/22/2197139_e04cc67ec49c90f5f454b1000eafb0df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F07%2F22%2F2197139_e04cc67ec49c90f5f454b1000eafb0df.jpg&h=cacadc27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac11fffe281d87888f35c2f70b887d2298d1bcd3","tid":2357384,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:46:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">涉違國安法等多人包括何啟明、劉偉聰等已獲准保釋離開</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569211-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569211-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z5ktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=9b25e32c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569211-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1aa8b460\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569211-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n50多名發起或參與民主派初選人士，涉嫌違反《香港國安法》昨日被捕，部分被捕人士陸續獲准保釋，其中兩名被捕的深水埗區議員，包括何啟明及劉偉聰晚上獲准保釋，離開深水埗警署。<br />\n<br />\n協調初選的戴耀廷被扣留在馬鞍山警署，他的太太晚上7時許抵達警署，獲告知要再等多2至3小時，之後離開。<br />\n<br />\n阿布泰國生活百貨創辦人林景楠亦被扣留在馬鞍山警署，他的家人晚上到警署。被扣留在油麻地警署的民主黨黃碧雲下午已交3萬元保釋金，等待指示離開。<br />\n<br />\n曾參與初選、正在服刑的前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒被安排到荔枝角懲教所錄口供。據了解，正還柙的人民力量副主席譚得志，亦因參與初選被捕。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨胡志偉原本獲准保釋，但警方在昨日的拘捕行動中，發現他未有按要求交出英國國民（海外）護照，涉嫌違反另一宗案件的保釋條件，下午被轉介到西九龍裁判法院應訊，裁判官將案件押後至明早10時半處理，他需要還押懲教署看管。"},{"pid":"1266eff4f7a742a805785ebcd71986de5d081a55","tid":2357384,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"劉偉聰 都拉, CLS！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4e048bdbe8a6a5dd4b2a7cb40b7e67d5acb8df","tid":2357384,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fd8ce3611a54694c667dc98d857edb5a95f8299","tid":2357384,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:42:40.000Z","msg":"又話好歹毒計劃？<br />\n<br />\n咁歹毒又可以保釋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:47:16.000Z","msg":"你保釋咗一定會做好多野，搵人跟下你，監控下你，又拉多一班"},{"pid":"d4a8549bd704120058d15bba66b3663d1714e26f","tid":2357384,"uid":46927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"有冇沒收護照"}]}